data.description: Pristine home in Cobblestone Park ready for a new owner! With an exterior mix of hardy plank and stone accents, you will find this beautiful home provides just over 2,000 sqft of living space. Enter in from the two-car garage or front door onto the main floor that is an open floor concept. Great room with high ceilings and a fireplace sit in tandem with the kitchen that provides large island with bar seating to compliment the open rooms. Outfitted kitchen with granite countertops, pantry space and a gas range make it an ideal spot for the chef in the family. Master suite on the main level elevates your ease of living with a private bathroom, double vanity, bidet, walk-in shower and large closet with built-ins. Two more bedrooms sit on either side of a full bath right off the front entrance. Additional suite in the FROG is perfect for guests, a play room or at-home office. Find your sweet spot for relaxing in the sun room at the back of the home where you can enjoy a good read or your morning coffee! Fenced-in back yard is great for the furry members of the family with plenty of space to roam and enjoy. Cobblestone Park is a wonderful community with various amenities like security, pool, tennis courts and more.
